        "text_roman": "Mujhse pehli-si mohabbat meri mehboob na maang\nMaine samjha tha ki tu hai to darakhshan hai hayat\n\nAur bhi dukh hain zamaane mein mohabbat ke siwa\nRahaten aur bhi hain vasl ki raahat ke siwa"
