        "text_roman": "Himadri tunga shringa se prabuddha shuddha bharati -\nSwayam prabha samujjwala swatantrata pukaarti!\n\nAmartya veer putra हो, dridh-patigya soch lo,\nPrashast punya panth hai, badhe chalo, badhe chalo!"
