        "text_roman": "Jago phir ek baar!\nSamar-sharat-sartaaj, shatru-dal-mardan,\nDheer-veer-gambheer, dheer tum, jago phir ek baar!\n\nPashu nahin, tum veer ho purush-singh ho,\nChalo bahti hui hawa mein bhar do hunkaar."
